{"id": 1341, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年错过了什么让你觉得遗憾？", "description": "一个白日梦：后悔药和时光机，哪个会先被发明出来？（题图来自：Josh Holinaty）", "record_count": 3237, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161123150416dI4yD7L0cam6s95A.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-10T17:00:46Z", "options": [{"id": 142592, "content": "错过了很多，但大多都是自己做的决定，遗憾倒算不上", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601413}, {"id": 142848, "content": "错过了学位授予仪式，错过了毕业旅行，错过了很多很多有可能在我生命里留下重要印记的人，错过了大把可以好好珍惜的时间……", "image": "img/option/option/20161211182647dScvpsmKeMARN5Co.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864157}, {"id": 143104, "content": "没有遗憾哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769270}, {"id": 146944, "content": "怀孕升职，全错过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 878710}, {"id": 142849, "content": "高考", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 862588}, {"id": 143105, "content": "还错过了看一场明星演唱会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620145}, {"id": 143361, "content": "错过了握在手中却流失于指缝的2016。好想时间过的再慢一点，我就能不这么遗憾了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865039}, {"id": 142594, "content": "错过了周杰伦的演唱会", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392268}, {"id": 142850, "content": "和女朋友分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741228}, {"id": 143618, "content": "某个人的最后一面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676832}, {"id": 143874, "content": "一本", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865541}, {"id": 150274, "content": "那个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889204}, {"id": 142595, "content": "没有好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392268}, {"id": 142851, "content": "没和淑芬说过话…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717256}, {"id": 143107, "content": "命运总是捉弄于人。机缘总是把控不好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620145}, {"id": 142596, "content": "总是不够坚持", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392268}, {"id": 142852, "content": "高考填志愿，不知道到底算是错过还算是缘分", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655962}, {"id": 143108, "content": "篮球队面试", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674726}, {"id": 142597, "content": "没有改变任何一个坏习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392268}, {"id": 142853, "content": "错过了\n她", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864168}, {"id": 143109, "content": "爱情\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847843}, {"id": 154885, "content": "没把前些年的计划完成", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683449}, {"id": 142598, "content": "时光机", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813380}, {"id": 142854, "content": "明明工資過萬 但3年過去了都沒存款 上個月才想起要存錢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408949}, {"id": 143110, "content": "错过了在该年龄该做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864463}, {"id": 143878, "content": "没有疯狂地练习口语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858768}, {"id": 142599, "content": "不该发后面那几封邮件", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863764}, {"id": 142855, "content": "我拥有的都是侥幸啊我失去的都是人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864167}, {"id": 143111, "content": "发财", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 373125}, {"id": 143623, "content": "再一次，错过了家乡的春秋。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865597}, {"id": 143879, "content": "还是没有学会相信别人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866904}, {"id": 142600, "content": "在地铁上没有看好自己的手机，我的照片啊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863766}, {"id": 142856, "content": "错过了一个男票？", "image": "img/option/option/20161211182856OQkf7SPFoV058sDq.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 37770}, {"id": 143112, "content": "错过了冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864473}, {"id": 143880, "content": "司法考试?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866905}, {"id": 142601, "content": "错过了，自己最后一次的决定做的太晚！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857394}, {"id": 142857, "content": "错过自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733095}, {"id": 143113, "content": "错过了好运", "image": "img/option/option/201612112219207wWFiNcJ6Ql2h8AM.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708972}, {"id": 142602, "content": "都是自己造成的错过，却没有想要挽回", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863203}, {"id": 142858, "content": "高考失利 要重新奋斗一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863414}, {"id": 152330, "content": "啥也没干", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898952}, {"id": 142603, "content": "李安的120桢", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673194}, {"id": 142859, "content": "错过了如果，没有错过，不是过错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811660}, {"id": 143115, "content": "没有好好复习四级", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864474}, {"id": 143883, "content": "可以免费去看曼城德比，但是我他吗没有护照", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 866953}, {"id": 152075, "content": "没能入民乐团。遗憾。太遗憾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897997}, {"id": 142860, "content": "应该早点分手?? 尽管3月就分了但是明明不该留着过年！今年决定了挺多重要的事情，生活方式也有大的改变，总体来说没什么遗憾嘻嘻！希望继续保持~然后来年目标希望能完成哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813628}, {"id": 143116, "content": "没有珍惜你爱和爱你的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826034}, {"id": 152076, "content": "对别人表白了。结果他只当我是朋友，太冲动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897997}, {"id": 142861, "content": "错过了和他把误会说清楚的机会\n也许是他根本不想听了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720448}]}